* New case

--
Communicated by:
ProMED-mail
<promed@promedmail.org>

[A ongoing puzzle. Logically the remaining contaminated heroin has
been stashed away and has yet to be used up. A pity that the
authorities cannot offer to buy it in confidence to get it off the
street. There is some evidence for latent infections in this disease
and one might therefore speculatively wonder whether this is
occurring here -- in the absence of specific information from these
late cases. On what we are seeing it would be unwise to bet that this
is the very last case in this series. - Mod.MHJ]
